OL,3,CAlleged Golders Green attacker faces
OL,4,Ctrial next year
OL,6,FThe alleged Golders Green attacker,
OL,7,Fwho is accused of stabbing two men in
OL,8,Fa north London street, is set to face
OL,9,Ftrial next year.
OL,11,FEssa Suleiman, 45, allegedly targeted
OL,12,FShloime Rand, 34, and Norman Shine,
OL,13,F76, during a knife rampage on
OL,14,FWednesday, April 29.
OL,16,FBefore travelling to Golders Green, he
OL,17,Fallegedly attacked a friend of 20
OL,18,Fyears at his home in Southwark, south
OL,19,FLondon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
