OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778933513
OL,3,CAlleged Golders Green attacker faces
OL,4,Ctrial next year
OL,6,FThe Somalia-born defendant was charged
OL,7,Fwith three counts of attempted murder
OL,8,Fand possessing a black-handled knife
OL,9,Fin a public place.
OL,11,FHe appeared by videolink from Belmarsh
OL,12,Fhigh-security prison at the Old Bailey
OL,13,Fon Friday for a preliminary hearing
OL,14,Fbefore Mrs Justice Cheema-Grubb.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
