OL,3,CAlleged Golders Green attacker faces
OL,4,Ctrial next year
OL,6,FSetting out the allegations against
OL,7,Fhim, prosecutor Deanna Heer KC said:
OL,8,F"The case arises out of events that
OL,9,Foccurred on April 29, 2026 when Mr
OL,10,FSuleiman firstly attended an address
OL,11,Fin south London where he attacked a
OL,12,Ffriend of his, Mr Hussein, with a
OL,13,Fknife at his home address.
OL,15,F"Having left that location, he then
OL,16,Fmade his way by public transport to
OL,17,Fthe area of Golders Green, where he
OL,18,Fwas seen mid-morning on Highfield
OL,19,FAvenue in Golders Green.
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778933513
OL,3,CAlleged Golders Green attacker faces
OL,4,Ctrial next year
OL,6,F"He then set about attacking two
OL,7,Fpeople both of whom were obviously
OL,8,Fmembers of the orthodox Jewish
OL,9,Fcommunity by the way they were dressed
OL,10,Fat the time.
OL,12,F"The first, Shloime Rand, 34, had been
OL,13,Fstudying at a synagogue in Highfield
OL,14,FAvenue. He was attacked by the
OL,15,Fdefendant who came towards him,
OL,16,Fstabbed him once to the chest, causing
OL,17,Fa punctured lung.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778933513
OL,3,CAlleged Golders Green attacker faces
OL,4,Ctrial next year
OL,6,F"The defendant then attacked Norman
OL,7,FShine, 76, also wearing Jewish
OL,8,Fclothing. Mr Shine sustained a number
OL,9,Fof stab wounds which caused him to be
OL,10,Ftaken to hospital where he remained
OL,11,Ffor several days."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FMs Heer said Mr Shine had suffered
OL,19,Fseveral stab wounds, including to the
OL,20,Fneck.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
