OL,3,CAlleged Golders Green attacker faces
OL,4,Ctrial next year
OL,6,FShe added: "The incident came to an
OL,7,Fend when another member of the public
OL,8,Fintervened to try to disarm the
OL,9,Fdefendant and take the knife from him."
OL,11,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb set a plea
OL,12,Fhearing for September 25 and a
OL,13,Fprovisional three-week trial at the
OL,14,FOld Bailey from March 1 2027.
OL,16,FSuleiman, who had previously been
OL,17,Fliving in supported accommodation in
OL,18,Fsouth London, was remanded into
OL,19,Fcustody before his next hearing.
OL,26,@nD@LOU
